PEOPLE
v.
S.C. (WALKER) S243072 Supreme Court of California FEBRUARY 28, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

**525The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division One, with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the *344cause in light of People v. Superior Court (Lara) (2018) 4 Cal.5th 299, 228 Cal.Rptr.3d 394, 410 P.3d 22. ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
